---
title: Double Seared Beef Rump & Peanut-Soy Sauce with Roast Veggie Chunks & Crisp Pear Slaw
description: Get a little crazy with beef steak and veggies by adding a nutty soy sauce over the beef. The pop of garlic will get your taste buds excited for the next bite. If you need a moment of peace, the fresh pear slaw is sure to balance the dish out. You’ll never want your steak and veggies any other way!
